::Dion::

"I'm hangin'," Dion says, placing his hands against the wall and feeling his fingers heat up and his hands begin to sink into it, but knowing that he wasn't fast enough. Seconds before the crash, he mutters an activation code, transforming into a lowrider inside the hallway, bending and breaking the walls and getting himself stuck as the ship crashes. After the shaking stops, he transforms back, the hallway collapsing behind him.

"Yeah, let's go," he replies to Repungus, walking along with him.
